{
  "stem": "3638.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish, there was the-- like a Jewish wel-- not welfare.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You call it here welfare, but over there it was Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the president--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "President and all the other thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would not remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All I remember is was one of them was Simcha Spira.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Simcha Spira-- how do you spell it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "S-I-M-C-H-A, Spira, S-P-I-R-A.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the-- he was the president of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was later on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before that, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one-- oh yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was one by the name of Rubinstein, R-U-B-I-N-S-T-E-I-N.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was, before the war, a teacher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was, I think, president or something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They formed the Judenrat straightaway, as soon as the German came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they could not go to individual Jew what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to the Judenrat and the Judenrat went to the Jews and demanded what-- whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they went to the Judenrat, and they tell them that they want that, and that day all the Jews should wear the armband.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Judenrat went and he put up-- put up all the sign.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and announce it, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was not a radio announce or television.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just they had paper, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Posted on every corner, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's where they demand the furs, so they did it the same way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They posted and everybody had to go get.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they want jewelry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right from the beginning, the first, they said anybody who would be find with a weapon would be shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was right-- I've forgotten to tell you-- that's right from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
